    {
      "page_number": 2,
      "width": 595.4400024414062,
      "height": 841.6799926757812,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b0",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            503.3399963378906,
            19.427974700927734,
            543.3359985351562,
            52.512001037597656
          ],
          "text": "Annex",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b1",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.5,
            66.76800537109375,
            543.3360595703125,
            97.87198638916016
          ],
          "text": "1. Penal interest for Delayed Reporting / Wrong Reporting / Non-Reporting of \nCurrency Chest Transactions",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b2",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.5,
            108.468017578125,
            352.2397766113281,
            125.65201568603516
          ],
          "text": "1.1  \nReporting of Currency Chest Transactions",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b3",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.5,
            136.44004821777344,
            546.6959838867188,
            169.08004760742188
          ],
          "text": "The minimum amount of deposit into / withdrawal from currency chest will be ` 1,00,000  \nand thereafter, in multiples of ` 50,000.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b4",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.5,
            182.6280517578125,
            242.13726806640625,
            199.81204223632812
          ],
          "text": "1.2  \nTime limit for Reporting",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b5",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.5,
            210.3480224609375,
            543.3409423828125,
            243.43203735351562
          ],
          "text": "1.2.1 The currency chests / Link Offices should invariably report all transactions through \nCyM – CC portal on the same day by 7 pm.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b6",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.5,
            256.1280517578125,
            543.33984375,
            289.1520690917969
          ],
          "text": "1.2.2 The Sub-Treasury Offices (STOs) should report all transactions directly to the \nIssue Office of the Reserve Bank by 7 pm on the same day.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b7",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.5,
            301.9080810546875,
            369.5159912109375,
            319.0920715332031
          ],
          "text": "1.2.3 Relaxation in respect of strike period in banks",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b8",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            103.5,
            329.820068359375,
            543.3397827148438,
            362.1000671386719
          ],
          "text": "Relaxation in the reporting period on account of strike situation will be considered \non case-to-case basis.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b15",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            237.08990478515625,
            360.2225341796875,
            357.62628173828125,
            480.7589111328125
          ],
          "text": "Withdrawn",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 28.0,
            "name": "Arial",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b9",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.50001525878906,
            375.4080810546875,
            240.15724182128906,
            392.5920715332031
          ],
          "text": "1.3 \nLevy of penal interest –",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b10",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.50001525878906,
            405.2880859375,
            250.83602905273438,
            422.4720764160156
          ],
          "text": "1.3.1 Delay in Reporting -",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b11",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            103.5,
            435.3000793457031,
            543.3433837890625,
            531.0001220703125
          ],
          "text": "In the event of delay in reporting currency chest transactions, penal interest at the \nrate indicated in paragraph 3 of this circular will be levied on the amount due \nfrom the chest holding bank for the period of delay. Penal interest will be \ncalculated on T+0 basis i.e. penal interest will be levied in respect of transactions \nnot reported by currency chests / Link Offices to the Issue Office on the same \nbusiness day within the time limit prescribed above.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b12",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            103.49996948242188,
            544.5001220703125,
            543.3372192382812,
            576.7800903320312
          ],
          "text": "Penal interest will also be charged for delay in reporting by STOs directly linked to \nIssue Department of the circle.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b13",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.5,
            590.1480712890625,
            200.79598999023438,
            607.3320922851562
          ],
          "text": "1.3.2 Wrong reporting",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b14",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            103.49999237060547,
            620.10009765625,
            543.3411865234375,
            764.0520629882812
          ],
          "text": "Penal interest will be levied in respect of cases of wrong reporting in the same \nmanner till the date of receipt of corrected advice by Reserve Bank. As \ndebits/credits to banks' current accounts are raised on the basis of the \ntransactions reported by the currency chests / Link Offices, penal interest will \ninvariably be levied in all cases of wrong reporting by the currency chests. It is \nexpected that currency chests / Link Offices would ensure the correctness of \nfigures reported on the CyM - CC portal. Particular care should be taken to ensure \nthat remittances of fresh notes/notes to the currency chests are not reported as \n'deposit' transactions on the portal.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        }
      ],
      "links": []
    },
    {
      "page_number": 3,
      "width": 595.4400024414062,
      "height": 841.6799926757812,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b0",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.5,
            33.408016204833984,
            543.3386840820312,
            64.4520034790039
          ],
          "text": "1.3.3 Penal interest for inclusion of ineligible amounts in the currency chest \nbalances",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b1",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.5,
            75.17997741699219,
            543.3399047851562,
            170.88009643554688
          ],
          "text": "(i) \nPenal interest will be levied in all cases where the bank has enjoyed 'ineligible' \ncredit in its current account with Reserve Bank on account of wrong reporting / \ndelayed reporting / non-reporting of transactions.  Penal measures will also be \ntaken in cases of shortages in chest balances / remittances, shortages due to \npilferage / frauds, counterfeit banknotes detected in chest balances / remittances \nas per the prevailing “Scheme of Penalties”.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b2",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.5,
            184.38011169433594,
            543.3446655273438,
            311.8202819824219
          ],
          "text": "(ii) \nFurther, only cash held in the custody of joint custodians and 'freely available' to \nthem is eligible for inclusion in the chest balances. Thus, cash kept for safe \ncustody in sealed covers for whatever reasons/cash in trunks/bins under the lock \nand key of any official/s other than the Joint Custodians or bearing a third lock put \nby any official in addition to the two locks of the Joint Custodians is not eligible for \nbeing included in the chest balances. If such amounts are included in the chest \nbalances, these will be treated as instances of wrong reporting and will attract \npenal interest at the rate specified in Para 3.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b3",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.5,
            325.3202819824219,
            543.3435668945312,
            452.82025146484375
          ],
          "text": "(iii) \nIn all the above cases (excepting shortages in chest balances / remittances, \nshortages due to pilferage / frauds, counterfeit banknotes detected in chest \nbalances / remittances), penal interest will be levied from the date of inclusion of \n'ineligible' amounts in chest balances till the exclusion of such amounts from chest \nbalances.  Penal measures for shortages in chest balances / remittances, \nshortages due to pilferage / frauds, counterfeit banknotes detected in chest \nbalances / remittances will be taken on the basis of prevailing “Scheme of \nPenalties”.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b9",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            237.08990478515625,
            360.2225341796875,
            357.62628173828125,
            480.7589111328125
          ],
          "text": "Withdrawn",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 28.0,
            "name": "Arial",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b4",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            66.72000122070312,
            466.1282653808594,
            194.1959991455078,
            483.312255859375
          ],
          "text": "2 \nLevy of penalty",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b5",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            66.72000122070312,
            496.0082702636719,
            358.8359680175781,
            513.1922607421875
          ],
          "text": "2.1 \nReporting of Soiled note remittances to RBI",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b6",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            103.5,
            526.020263671875,
            543.3386840820312,
            590.3402709960938
          ],
          "text": "Soiled note remittances to RBI should not be shown as withdrawal by chest/s / \nlink offices. In case such remittances to RBI are wrongly reported as 'withdrawals', \na penalty of ` 50,000 will be levied irrespective of the value of remittance and \nperiod of such wrong reporting.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b7",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            66.72003173828125,
            603.708251953125,
            358.176025390625,
            620.8922729492188
          ],
          "text": "2.2 \nReporting of diversions in CyM – CC portal",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b8",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            103.50003051757812,
            633.6602783203125,
            543.3385009765625,
            729.7202758789062
          ],
          "text": "All currency chest diversions (both between chests of the same bank and \nbetween chests of different banks) have to be reported through ‘Diversion Module’ \nof CyM-CC Portal. The CC sending the diversion should initiate the diversion \nentry. The receiving CC should acknowledge the same. Diversions must not be \nreported as Deposit/Withdrawal.  A penalty of ` 50,000 will be levied for such \nwrong reporting.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        }
      ],
      "links": []
    },
    {
      "page_number": 4,
      "width": 595.4400024414062,
      "height": 841.6799926757812,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "block_id": "p4_b0",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            66.72000122070312,
            65.38800048828125,
            448.89599609375,
            82.5719985961914
          ],
          "text": "2.3 \nDelayed reporting where currency chests had “Net Deposit”",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p4_b1",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            103.5,
            95.40000915527344,
            543.3421630859375,
            175.56008911132812
          ],
          "text": "Penal interest at the prevailing rate for delayed reporting of the instances where \nthe currency chest had reported “net deposit” may not be charged.  However, in \norder to ensure proper discipline in reporting currency chest transactions, a flat \npenalty of ` 50,000 may be levied on the currency chests for delayed reporting \nirrespective of the value of net deposit.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p4_b2",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.5,
            188.9281005859375,
            228.87600708007812,
            206.11209106445312
          ],
          "text": "3.  \nRate of penal interest",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p4_b3",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            103.5,
            216.84007263183594,
            543.3399047851562,
            264.9601135253906
          ],
          "text": "Penal interest shall be levied at the rate of 2% over the prevailing Bank Rate for \nthe period of delayed reporting/wrong reporting/non-reporting /inclusion of \nineligible amounts in chest balances.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p4_b4",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.5,
            278.328125,
            474.87994384765625,
            295.5121154785156
          ],
          "text": "4.  \nLevy of penal interest in respect of currency chests at treasuries",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p4_b5",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            103.5,
            306.2400817871094,
            540.041015625,
            338.52008056640625
          ],
          "text": "The above instructions shall be applicable to currency chests at treasury/sub-\ntreasury offices also.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p4_b6",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.5,
            351.8280944824219,
            200.85601806640625,
            369.0120849609375
          ],
          "text": "5.  \nRepresentations",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p4_b11",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            237.08990478515625,
            360.2225341796875,
            357.62628173828125,
            480.7589111328125
          ],
          "text": "Withdrawn",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 28.0,
            "name": "Arial",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p4_b7",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.5,
            379.60809326171875,
            543.33984375,
            491.4000549316406
          ],
          "text": "5.1 \nAs the sole criterion for levy of penal interest for delayed reporting is the number \nof days of delay, there should ordinarily be no occasion for banks to request for \nreconsideration of the Reserve Bank's decision in individual cases. However, \nrepresentations, if any, on account of genuine difficulties faced by chests \nespecially in hilly/remote areas and those affected by natural calamities, etc., may \nbe made to the Issue Office concerned through the Head / Controlling office of the \nbank concerned within a month from the date of debit of the bank concerned.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p4_b8",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.5,
            504.6480712890625,
            543.338623046875,
            537.1201171875
          ],
          "text": "5.2 \nIn the case of wrong reporting representations for waiver will not be considered. \n{cf. para 1.3.2 above}.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p4_b9",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            66.72001647949219,
            550.4281005859375,
            543.3410034179688,
            678.06005859375
          ],
          "text": "5.3 \nAs the intention behind the levy of penal interest is to inculcate discipline among \nbanks so as to ensure prompt/correct reporting, pleas by banks for waiver of \npenal interest on grounds that delayed/wrong/non-reporting did not result in \nutilization of the Reserve Bank's funds or shortfall in the maintenance of \nCRR/SLR or that they were the result of  clerical mistakes, unintentional or \narithmetical errors, first time error, inexperience of staff etc., will not be \nconsidered as valid grounds for waiver of penal interest.  Further, we will take a \nserious view of all such lapses.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p4_b10",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            253.80001831054688,
            690.0480346679688,
            356.9880065917969,
            707.9760131835938
          ],
          "text": "-------------------------",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        }
      ],
